---
// Hero Nosotros - Sección hero para página Nosotros
---

<section class="relative min-h-[65vh] lg:min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-black pt-40 lg:pt-44">
  <!-- Background Image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src="/imagenes/imagen2.png" alt="S3A Industrial" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/50 via-black/30 to-black/60"></div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Background pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 10px, rgba(204, 163, 115, 0.05) 10px, rgba(204, 163, 115, 0.05) 20px);"></div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-10 xl:px-12 max-w-4xl relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center text-white" style="text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.7), 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav style="font-family: var(--font-body);" class="text-xs md:text-sm mb-6 opacity-90 tracking-wide">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-golden-light transition-colors font-medium">Inicio</a>
        <span class="mx-3">•</span>
        <span class="text-golden-light font-semibold">Nosotros</span>
      </nav>
      
      <!-- Title -->
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-display); letter-spacing: 0.03em;" class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-normal mb-8 leading-none uppercase">
        Quiénes Somos
      </h1>
      
      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body);" class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
        Conoce la historia, experiencia y valores que nos convierten en especialistas 
        en reparación y mantenimiento de sopladores industriales.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-golden opacity-20 blur-2xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-10 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-golden-light opacity-15 blur-xl"></div>
</section>